    metaDescription: "Compare MerrySails' main Bosphorus cruise prices for 2026: sunset €34 / €40, dinner €30–€90, [yacht charter](/yacht-charter-istanbul) from €220 per vessel, plus how custom quote daytime services fit into the structure.",
    excerpt: "How much does a Bosphorus cruise really cost in 2026? This guide now focuses on MerrySails' three core price ranges and explains where tailored daytime service pages sit in the pricing structure.",
